Source: pg-dbms-job
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), libpq-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/HexaCluster/pg_dbms_job

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-dbms-job
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-dbms-job
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Oracle-compatible DBMS_JOB scheduler for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pg_dbms_job provides transactional scheduled and asynchronous jobs through a
 per-database background worker compatible with the Oracle DBMS_JOB interface.
